EU to Propose Coordinated Action on Bank Recapitalizations

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-06T10:43:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/eu-to-propose-coordinated-action-on-bank-recapitalizations.html
The European Union plans to propose
“coordinated action” on recapitalizing banks in the region.  “The commission will propose coordinated action on bank
recapitalization to member states,” Alejandro Ulzurrun de
Asanza y Munoz, a spokesman for the European Commission, the EU
executive, told reporters today in Brussels, reiterating
comments made earlier today by Commission President  Jose
Barroso . “We are making a proposal so that we can act together
in a coordinated fashion,” the spokesman said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jones Hayden at 
 jhayden1@bloomberg.net  